{"tid":1383131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫手解夢] 發夢見到呢個係咩意思","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T15:53:26.000Z","uid":291331,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cdc84d0683fd97d3dee10ef770f04bc3db87dcf1","tid":1383131,"uid":291331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:37:28.000Z","msg":"對唔住我係P牌仔但我發夢夢到香港嘅大家都ready攬炒嘅故仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係無人癱瘓機場因為有旅客有人流<br />\n<br />\n之後有個男仔話不如去港交所吖,但係佢朋友就答無用㗎,因為依家所有資金流動上網㩒幾個制就搞掂, 去個公司參觀似乎無咩用<br />\n<br />\n之後我個夢就跳到去貨櫃碼頭出入口,見到好多人企喺到,啲貨物郁唔到,啲食物到唔到餐廳<br />\n<br />\n跟住我餓醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人幫我解釋吓點解個夢咁奇怪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84929d6044033e8ca45d114306c5711309881633","tid":1383131,"uid":291331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:39:24.000Z","msg":"有無人幫幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc51af82eef2ba2b6efd34891e9edea18b2fda05","tid":1383131,"uid":291331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ed686b9c4724bdf812e12c82143996339550f2","tid":1383131,"uid":2212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:42:42.000Z","msg":"N咁多個碼頭，無得搞"},{"pid":"29cee96f6cde4e2a1c0a4deb389a5923d9fcaa51","tid":1383131,"uid":291331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96ed686b9c4724bdf812e12c82143996339550f2","tid":1383131,"uid":2212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:42:42.000Z","msg":"N咁多個碼頭，無得搞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:46:29.000Z","msg":"sorry我唔記得讀夢入面嘅係葵青貨櫃碼頭,好似話係咩全球第八大貨櫃港"},{"pid":"f0c62cab01569a244f0999be3b785438889d64ff","tid":1383131,"uid":291331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579a6be47f82d85f12e4dfcea60c5a68673c6566","tid":1383131,"uid":291331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0ba7642541ee97ac9b0d77d98d30c1de550b03","tid":1383131,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:51:33.000Z","msg":"香港碼頭嘅櫃好多時係轉船，根本唔駛出碼頭，要上中國嘅櫃一早去曬鹽田港。更何況嗰個死位嚟，無民居無商業啲煙任用唔嬲，左右包抄你點走都無用，一係上公路一係跳海，仲未計你跳到入海都係得一個出海口，海狗可以一網打盡"},{"pid":"c48a8dae006d91f3a8fe50e32a127d6187706ca8","tid":1383131,"uid":291331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:51:51.000Z","msg":"有無人幫吓我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4065261963955c39bff2d9e57b7adeba0408eeb8","tid":1383131,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29cee96f6cde4e2a1c0a4deb389a5923d9fcaa51","tid":1383131,"uid":291331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96ed686b9c4724bdf812e12c82143996339550f2","tid":1383131,"uid":2212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:42:42.000Z","msg":"N咁多個碼頭，無得搞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:46:29.000Z","msg":"sorry我唔記得讀夢入面嘅係葵青貨櫃碼頭,好似話係咩全球第八大貨櫃港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"冇得搞架，地方大，冇補給，<br />\n冇交通"},{"pid":"edeb521450bffcfa990732a3af61c0f464ab51c4","tid":1383131,"uid":291331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:53:26.000Z","msg":"多謝你地幫我<br />\n個心舒服晒喇"}]}